                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Try this one:
<br />

<br />
What once was lost, has now been found;
<br />
but he who shall seek, will find it not,
<br />
though in the end, it will be there.
<br />

<br />
GL, have fun.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Or...
<br />

<br />
I cannot walk, but I can run, and I am always close behind.  What am I?
<br />

<br />
 Or....
<br />

<br />

<br />
A quest of love ends with me, 
<br />
yet I am made endlessly.
<br />
If I  drop I  say my name,
<br />
What am I?
<br />

<br />
  Or....
<br />

<br />
One hundred by fifty divided, the cypher rightly applied, gets one from nine
<br />

<br />

<br />
I'll stop there...</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=638180" target="_blank" class="postlink">Yeldar</a>
